title: Google\Cloud\AppEngine\V1\AutomaticScaling
name: AutomaticScaling

Automatic scaling is based on request rate, response latencies, and other application metrics.

params.name: data.cool_down_period
params.description: The time period that the Autoscaler should wait before it starts collecting information from a new instance. This prevents the autoscaler from collecting information when the instance is initializing, during which the collected usage would not be reliable. Only applicable in the App Engine flexible environment.
